# Try to extract the most relevant section: search for 'loss' and 'TDPO' in the first 15 pages
import re
with open('./22-TokenDPO/TokenDPO-main/paper.pdf', 'rb') as f:
    reader = PyPDF2.PdfReader(f)
    text = ''
    for page in reader.pages[:15]:
        text += page.extract_text() + '\n'

# Find all paragraphs containing 'loss' or 'TDPO'
loss_paragraphs = re.findall(r'([^.]*?(?:loss|TDPO)[^.]*\.)', text, re.IGNORECASE)
for para in loss_paragraphs:
    print(para.strip())
